fdt_parser

Module cache 

Source
Expand description

Cached FDT parser with indexed nodes for efficient lookups.

This module provides a cached representation of the device tree that builds an index for fast repeated lookups. It uses more memory than the direct parser but provides O(1) node access by path or phandle.
